Class ResultHighlighter

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class ResultHighlighter
extends LibrarySearchResultPane
    This class implements a simple result display where the results from the search are simply highlighted in the tree. Any subtree where a result may be located is also expanded.
    Author:
    Chad Berkley
